metadata.name: Undelivered Letters-01
metadata.description:
This token is an alternative to collecting my writings Undelivered Letters-01.

Mirror has fully switched to Optimism, so you can no longer collect articles using mainnet ETH. As an alternative, I am minting the sketch/illustration/banner on Manifold.  
They will be available for exactly the same price as the article. 

You can read the writing for free, collect the illustration, or collect the article in mirror.
